&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;Output&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;This pin can be used to supply power to the target hardware. Older J-Links may not be able to supply power on this pin. For more information about how to enable/disable the power supply, please refer to &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93aWtpLnNlZ2dlci5jb20vMjAtcGluX0otTGlua19Db25uZWN0b3IjVGFyZ2V0X3Bvd2VyX3N1cHBseQ==&#34;&gt;Target power supply&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/td&gt;
